    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You\u2019ve gotta see this absolute gem! It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly spectacular, showroom-ready condition. Seriously, it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so you\u2019re getting a ride that\u2019s practically flawless. If you\u2019re looking for a top-tier beauty that\u2019s ready for the road, this is the one for you! Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
