    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have seriously got to see this beauty in person\u2014it is absolutely flawless! It\u2019s been babied since day one and honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found; it is pure perfection. I'm so excited for the next owner to get behind the wheel of this gem. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44900.0,
