    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully overhauled for optimal cam timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has undergone comprehensive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. This vehicle remains in factory-original configuration with flawless Laguna Seca Blue paintwork and a pristine interior. Recent compression tests show consistent numbers across all cylinders, confirming the mechanical health of this naturally aspirated icon.",
